research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Littlefield, TX operates under a Mayor-Council form of government, with a City Council as its main governing body. The City Council also appoints a City Manager to handle administrative and executive affairs. There is a discrepancy in sources regarding the Council Member for District 2; the official city website lists Jason Ayala, while other sources, including the Texas State Directory and a recent news article, list Michael Rangel.
